<br>
I have no problems with the strategy with the bosses themself, but do you know the faster way ? Do you wait LDs (I hate those) ? Is there any places in the castle when you can make med the caster, while CoHing and waiting LDs ? <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#2F2F4F><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub14.ezboard.com/bthesteelwarrior.showUserPublicProfile?gid=eles@thesteelwarrior>Eles</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>knows that Warriors are superior</span><br>  Posts: 6<br> <font color=#FF0000>(11/16/02 8:23 pm)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: A guide for chardok (epic run to royals)</span><hr size=1> We have, at one time, CoH from the area right past the GY before you enter the palace. I do believe we had a guild xp group who had gone earlier that had come in and cleared it out a bit, and included the CoH mage. Then the druid succored to zone out, zoned and came back in. We CoH in the melee and a nother cleric first, kept on the spawns, and stormed the palace. It saves a bit of time. As for LD's, we dont really wait. We have one guy (a cleric incidentely) who is on very good terms with the people of chardok, and he drags any ld's who dont make it back reaaal fast, then rez's em. Hope that helps. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#000000><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub14.ezboard.com/bthesteelwarrior.showUserPublicProfile?gid=aarlonbladefury>Aarlon Bladefury</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>knows that Warriors are superior</span><br>  Posts: 66<br> <font color=#FF0000>(11/17/02 11:59 am)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: A guide for chardok (epic run to royals)</span><hr size=1> As a guild we just did the Royals in 5 pulls AE style.  The total raid took under an hour.  We are not an Uber guild by far.  We do WToV named but have yet to do NToV encounters.<br>
<br>
Here is how we did it with about 24 people (2 clerics, 3 chanters, 1 wizzy, 1 mage and rest were melee but no shaman or FD pullers).<br>
<br>
Mage suicides on a ZI mob and gets dragged around the corner from Prince lair by non KoS person.  This is the doorway leading to the hallway to the Library. Proceed to CoH raid force down but nobody move because the safe area is pretty small.  Buff up and pull Prince room and anything betwen him and you.  All melee focus on Prince while wizzy, mage and any druids AE the rest while chanters chain stun.<br>
<br>
Med up and pull the 6 guards in the tunnel to the library. AE them down.<br>
<br>
Pull the library upstairs and down to the hall you just cleared.  AE them down.<br>
<br>
After medding up someone fell into the pit trap as we were moving into the next hallway past the library so we unexpectantly AE'd down the King, his guards and every mob in the hallway before the secret wall to the King/Queen. Same beatdown as Prince.  Melee focus on King while AE'rs stun and AE the rest.<br>
<br>
Then we moved into the king room to med up for Queen.  Once ready, MT lead the charge and took the first AE.  All melee rushed into melee with the Queen while the chanters AE stunned the guards.  Instead of wizzy/mage druids AEing they went full offensive on Queen. Once Queen is dead mez/AE/split tank guards as needed.<br>
<br>
There you go...Five pulls and dead Royals <p>&lt;p align=&quot;center&quot;&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;http://www.circleofpride.com/members/lavondyss/Aarlon2.jpg&quot; width=&quot;238&quot;height=&quot;300&quot;&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;BR&gt;&lt;p align=&quot;center&quot;&gt;&lt;a target=&quot;new&quot; href=&quot;http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=64417&quot;&gt;Aarlon Bladefury - Warlord&lt;/a&gt;</p><i></i></td></tr></table> </td></tr></table> <table border=0 width=95%><tr><td align=left valign="top"> </td><td align=right valign="top"><a href="http://pub14.ezboard.com/fthesteelwarriorthebattlefield.showPrevMessage?topicID=1493.topic"> << Prev Topic</a>&nbsp;| <a href="http://pub14.ezboard.com/fthesteelwarriorthebattlefield.showNextMessage?topicID=1493.topic"> Next Topic >> </a><br><br></td></tr></table><br><table width=95% border=0><td valign="top"> <a href=http://pub14.ezboard.com/fthesteelwarriorthebattlefield.emailToFriend?topicID=1493.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/image/email.gif border=0 alt="Email This To a Friend"> Email This To a Friend</a><br> <a href=http://pub14.ezboard.com/fthesteelwarriorthebattlefield.threadControl?topicID=1493.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/professional/deleteThread.gif border=0 alt="Topic Control Image"> Topic Commands</a><br> <a href=http://pub14.ezboard.com/fthesteelwarriorthebattlefield.subscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=1493.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/ultimate/subscribe.gif width=20 height=20 border=0 alt="Click to receive email notification of replies"> Click to receive email notification of replies</a> <br>  <a href=http://pub14.ezboard.com/fthesteelwarriorthebattlefield.unsubscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=1493.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/ultimate/unsubscribe.gif width=20 height=20 border=0 alt="Click to stop receiving email notification of replies"> Click to stop receiving email notification of replies</a> <br> </td><td align=